  05 Aug 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> radius-0.7.4-r1.ebuild:
  Remove trailing '.' from DESCRIPTION.

  19 Apr 2014; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> radius-0.7.4-r1.ebuild:
  Add ruby21. Drop jruby due to kramdown no longer supporting our jruby
  version.

